Things vectis-build should do
=============================

Things to port from gbp-buildall
--------------------------------

* Build an unpacked source directory with debuild -S (on the host system?)
* Optionally use gbp and/or svn-buildpackage (on the host system?)
* Source-only builds
* Run mergechanges a lot
* Silence tracebacks for CalledProcessError

New things
----------

* Optionally build using obs-build (debootstrap + build)
* Optionally run autopkgtest, again in VMs
* A subcommand for running arbitrary commands in the guest?
* Bootstrap and extend OSTree trees
* Build Flatpak runtimes
